# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies6.rpy:14
translate german jamies6_be7de664:

    # gnd "I love kids."
    gnd "Ich liebe Kinder."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies6.rpy:15
translate german jamies6_7c12ffa9:

    # gnd "They're so non-judgmental and just naturally happy."
    gnd "Sie sind so vorurteilsfrei und einfach von Natur aus fröhlich."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies6.rpy:16
translate german jamies6_cdad04c3:

    # gnd "I think that the first few years of school are so important for laying a foundation for learning, and I want to do that."
    gnd "Ich finde, dass die ersten Schuljahre so wichtig sind, um eine Grundlage fürs Lernen zu schaffen, und das möchte ich tun."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies6.rpy:21
translate german jamies6_e238708f:

    # gnd "Thanks, [pcname], I hope so."
    gnd "Danke, [pcname], das hoffe ich."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies6.rpy:22
translate german jamies6_c24aa9e0:

    # gnd "I can't picture myself doing anything else."
    gnd "Ich kann mir nicht vorstellen, etwas anderes zu machen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies6.rpy:25
translate german jamies6_9e1302d3:

    # gnd "What? Really?"
    gnd "Was? Wirklich?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies6.rpy:26
translate german jamies6_bfcce5e2:

    # pc "Yeah, they're all dirty and loud and obnoxious."
    pc "Ja, die sind alle schmutzig und laut und nervig."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies6.rpy:27
translate german jamies6_17cf9e3e:

    # gnd "No, not all of them are like that."
    gnd "Nein, nicht alle sind so."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies6.rpy:28
translate german jamies6_565133e0:

    # gnd "And usually from what I've seen the ones that are like that act that way because their parents are dirty, loud, and obnoxious."
    gnd "Und meistens, soweit ich das gesehen habe, verhalten sich die, die so sind, so, weil ihre Eltern schmutzig, laut und nervig sind."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies6.rpy:29
translate german jamies6_3426b7f9:

    # gnd "Most kids that I've dealt with have all been sweet and friendly and funny."
    gnd "Die meisten Kinder, mit denen ich zu tun hatte, waren alle lieb, freundlich und lustig."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies6.rpy:30
translate german jamies6_7650139a:

    # pc "Well I don't like them."
    pc "Na ja, ich mag sie nicht."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies6.rpy:31
translate german jamies6_1d4350b3:

    # gnd "Wow. That sucks. Kids are really important to me."
    gnd "Wow. Das ist ja schade. Kinder sind mir wirklich wichtig."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies6.rpy:33
translate german jamies6_bbe82b49:

    # gnd "Let's talk about something else before this ruins my night."
    gnd "Lass uns über etwas anderes reden, bevor das mir den Abend ruiniert."

